{"tid":467052,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵拳7宣布FFXV主角將作為第3波DlC角色登場","createTime":"2017-11-13T06:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T02:03:04.000Z","uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0ae7c2a48053a40b0b2553ff362e118f1d8f67","tid":467052,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment 於美國時間 12 日舉辦的鐵拳世界巡迴賽中宣布，系列最新作《鐵拳 7（Tekken 7）》將於 2018 年春季釋出第 3 波 DLC，加入 SQUARE ENIX 暢銷角色扮演遊戲《Final Fantasy XV》的主角「諾克提斯&middot;路希斯&middot;切拉姆（Noctis Lucis Caelum）」。<br />\n<br />\n　　從目前公布的揭露影片中，可以得知諾克提斯是接受好友拉斯（Lars）的請託處理格鬥與狩獵任務。對戰中他將施展熟悉的幻影劍與魔法，以移形換位的能力應戰。除了角色之外，還會加入《Final Fantasy XV》經典場景的格鬥擂台－席德妮（Cidney）經營的加油維修站「鎚頭鯊」。<br />\n <br />\n　　《鐵拳 7》DLC 3 預定 2018 年春季釋出，將收錄新角色「諾克提斯」與新場景「鎚頭鯊」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LmWbiMwxmOU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLmWbiMwxmOU&d=k57gxErVPdcx3EMewoHKXzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7ca760e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LmWbiMwxmOU</a>"},{"pid":"810846a819a7b9fc3d8263b56759b9887cdb549e","tid":467052,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"C L S"},{"pid":"7807467f644d505af595de2d37cb09f69abd495a","tid":467052,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"對上兩個DLC角色<br />\n<br />\n1. Akuma (Street Fighter)<br />\n2. Geese Howard (Fatal Fury)"},{"pid":"69380b5f7a7a6f306701d4c47d393a3c0aee68a1","tid":467052,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfga/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongfga%2F&d=k57gxErVPdcx3EMewoHKXzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=911f4654\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfga/</a><br />\n有興趣可以支持下格game page<br />\n想學鐵拳可以搵我同一班朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj